	<h4>Biography</h4>
	<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; I am an artist currently living in and working out of Montclair, New Jersey.  I graduated from Mason Gross School of Art at Rutgers University with a degree in Fine Art in 2001.  Soon after, I went back to school and received my teaching degree from Jersey City University.  I currently teach fine art at a high school in northern New Jersey.  For the past few years I have been showing my artwork in the New Jersey/New York area.  With this website I am trying to provide a large variety of work that best represents me as an artist.</p>

	<p>For any inquiries or comments feel free to contact me at <a href="mailto:mikeferrari@live.com">mikeferrari@live.com</a></p>

	<p>Enjoy.</p>

